title: 829. Kayvon Thibodeaux on Being a Pro & Playing for the Giants
itunes:title: 829. Kayvon Thibodeaux on Being a Pro & Playing for the Giants
description:
Bucky Brooks is back with a new episode of Move the Sticks with Giants edge rusher Kayvon Thibodeaux as a guest. Throughout the show, Thibodeaux hits on what it was like being drafted by the Giants on draft night, his first conversations with head coach Brian Daboll, what he's doing in the community, his role with the Giants, goals for his first season, and much more.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
